{"tid":744472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(最後今天)  連登登凳","createTime":"2018-07-16T03:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T03:38:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86fa83f711bbdd6b47479556f7c47c4169555bf4","tid":744472,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.singtao.com.au/wp-content/uploads/australia/2018/06/wpid-20180615134547254772.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2018%2F06%2Fwpid-20180615134547254772.jpg&h=ca958211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府今日起為10個委員會，招募青年人參與「青年委員自薦計畫」。青年發展委員會正副主席張建宗和劉鳴煒粉墨登場，拍廣告宣傳計畫。<br />\n<br />\n片中，張建宗問劉鳴煒知道甚麼是「登登登凳」後，不同的年輕委員會委員都圍著一張空凳，指這張凳要自己爭取。最後，張建宗稱「你的椅子已準備好了」，劉鳴煒接著表示我們「等你埋位」。<br />\n<br />\n「青年委員自薦計畫」今日開始公開招募青年人參與，申請截止日期為下月16日。參與計畫的委員會共有10個，各開放兩個名額予申請。招募工作預計於今年第4季完成。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局發言人表示，邀請於今年7月16日（即申請截止日期）當日年齡介乎18至35歲的青年人自薦成為上述10個委員會的委員。「自薦計畫」的申請表和具體詳情已上載於民政事務局網頁（<a href=\"http://www.hab.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hab.gov.hk&d=YANgR46M55LsrvAyiDZ4Jk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=547e74b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hab.gov.hk</a>）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.com.au/172-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82/467576-%E3%80%9018%E8%87%B335%E6%AD%B2%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E3%80%91%E8%87%AA%E8%96%A6%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E5%8A%89%E9%B3%B4%E7%85%92%E3%80%8C%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%A0%E5%9F%8B%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%8D/?fromG=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com.au%2F172-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%2F467576-%25E3%2580%259018%25E8%2587%25B335%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%2584%258F%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%2596%25A6%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2596%258B-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E7%2585%2592%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%259F%258B%25E4%25BD%258D%25E3%2580%258D%2F%3FfromG%3D1&d=YANgR46M55LsrvAyiDZ4Jk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=959beb22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.com.au/172-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82/467576-%E3%80%9018%E8%87%B335%E6%AD%B2%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E3%80%91%E8%87%AA%E8%96%A6%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E5%8A%89%E9%B3%B4%E7%85%92%E3%80%8C%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%A0%E5%9F%8B%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%8D/?fromG=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bb666916c9c91d7ab02c80368f1bd4ba9affd9","tid":744472,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"假諮詢做騷位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8985cf7eb22103fa28e70661258f97c15356843b","tid":744472,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"我都算係個五毛<br />\n唔知做唔做到呢"}]}